Very important for Martin van Cleve etc.; Hans MIELKE, 'Antwerpener Graphik in der 2. Hälfte des 16. Jahrhundert. Der "Thesaurus veteris et novi testamenti" des Gerard de Jode (1585) und seine Künstler', Zeitschrift für Kunstgeschichte 38, 1975, Heft 1, pp. 29-83, figs. 42-55 by or attr.to M. van Cleve. Also some engravings after designs by M. de Vos develop. Among the M. van Cleve drawings, Fig. 50 'Vogelsteller, Darmstadt, close to Bruegel; Include Vredeman de Vries in paper on Bruegel & with Balten & M. van Cleve.
